Package: netcutter
Type: Package
Title: Identification and Analysis of Co-Occurrence Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Heiko", "Müller", role = "aut"),
    person("Francesco", "Mancuso", role = "aut"),
    person("Federico", "Marotta", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Federico Marotta <federico.marotta@embl.de>
Description: R implementation of the NetCutter algorithm described in
    "H. Müller, F. Mancuso, Identification and analysis of co-occurrence
    networks with NetCutter. PLoS ONE 3, e3178 (2008)." The package identifies
    co-occurring terms in a list of containers. For example, it may be used
    to detect genes that co-occur across genomes.
URL: https://github.com/fmarotta/netcutter
BugReports: https://github.com/fmarotta/netcutter/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: PoissonBinomial
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
